//FAQFEEDBACK Error while checking the availability of rooms i cant find my current room(s) booking Can i share my Jamru Account?
You want to book a room but you cant see the availability? This is most likely happen due to unstable internet connection or full mobile memory capacity. You can always see your ongoing booking under "Booked" For a safety reason, we do not recommend you to share your account between users.
